Name Weapon - thematic skill
------------------------------------------------------------
This command will 'name' most generic weapons.  This is only
a cosmetic change; in order to prevent possible abuse, the
weapon will NOT ID to its name, except for the purposes of
the 'wield' and 'unwield' commands, where the weapon may be
referred to by the capitalized version of its name.

Wielding a weapon named with this skill gives a swashbuckler
an additional chance to gain Flair during combat.

Please use discretion with this ability, just as with selecting
a title after level 20.  Abuses will not be tolerated.

GL:  1 (It's essentially an emote.)
SP:  0
command:  nameweapon <weapon> to <name>
duration: permanent
see also: flair
